            options: ["not use", "didn‚Äôt use", "don‚Äôt use", "hadn‚Äôt used"], 
            correct: 1, 
            level: "B2",
            topic: "Unreal Past (I'd rather)" 
            },
            { 
            q: "9. The company is said ___ been founded in the 18th century.", 
            options: ["to", "to have", "to have been", "having been"], 
            correct: 1, // La opci√≥n correcta es 'to have' (to have + been founded)
            level: "C1",
            topic: "Passive (Perfect Infinitive)" 
            },
            { 
            q: "10. Little ___ that his decision would change the course of history.", 
            options: ["he knew", "did he know", "has he known", "he had known"], 
            correct: 1, 
